description: Going back to the scoop of this writing, it all depends on where you see it from, for a person the chaos generated by calm means comfort, despite dying slowly motionless, for them it is nothing but calm, they completely ignore the fact of dying and are content to just stop and adopt it as a new lifestyle, a chaos disguised as false peace, or well, for them it is real peace, that if anyone reads this, they would tell me that I want to disguise it as chaos... it all depends on what angle you see it from, or want to see it...
